    "body": "When main thread switches to a task, `kernel_task_entry` enters, making the call stack a fresh new one, the debugger still runs.\n\nBut when  `kernel_task_entry` returns, the debugger successfully exits, while it should jump back to the main thread (or jump to another task, though multiple users tasks haven't been tested yet).\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5ebf32ae-ffcc-4ec9-a554-7ed22da3b006",
